===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 67 people, 24 households, and 10 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A14475&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A14475&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The [[population density]] was 89.7 inhabitants per square mile (34.6/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 33 housing units at an average density of 44.2 per square mile (17.1/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age in the city was 41.5 years. 22.4% of residents were under the age of 20; 3.0% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 29.9% were from 25 and 44; 20.9% were from 45 and 64; and 23.9% were 65 years of age or older. 20.9% of residents were under the age of 18. The gender makeup of the city was 55.2% male and 44.8% female. For every 100 females there were 123.3 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 130.4 males.<ref name="Census2020DP"/> All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A14475&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of the 24 households, 20.8% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 33.3% were [[Marriage|married couples]] living together, 16.7% were cohabitating couples, 12.5% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present, and 37.5% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present. 58.3% of all households were non-families. 41.7% of all households were made up of individuals, and 20.8% had someone living alone who was 65 years old or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

Of the 33 housing units, 27.3% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 33.3%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

